description: Log-transformed intrinsic growth rate for COTS outbreaks (year^-1). Initial guess on log scale.
Log-transformed decline rate after outbreak for COTS (year^-1). Reflects density-dependent mortality.
Log-transformed intrinsic growth rate for coral species (year^-1), assumed same for fast and slow corals.
Efficiency of COTS predation on fast-growing coral (unitless, 0 to 1).
Efficiency of COTS predation on slow-growing coral (unitless, 0 to 1).
Threshold value for resource limitation in coral growth (% cover).
Modifier of COTS growth rate based on sea surface temperature deviations (unitless).
